summary_stat <- df %>% 
  dplyr::select(GAs, WAs, SAs, SPAs, SAoAs, SAoFe) %>%
  dplyr::summarise_all(list(Min = ~round(min(.), 2), 
                      Q25 = ~round(quantile(., 0.25), 2), 
                      Median = ~round(median(.), 2), 
                      Q75 = ~round(quantile(., 0.75), 2), 
                      Max = ~round(max(.), 2),
                      Mean = ~round(mean(.), 2), 
                      SD = ~round(sd(.), 3))) %>% 
  tidyr::pivot_longer(everything(), 
                      names_sep = "_",
